6:
Heed me, stars! Unravel what stands
before us!
12:
Unravel our curse, that we may yet
again find hope!
16: This light... Where is it coming from?
20:
Nephtim understands! The night
ends at last.
24: Alk and the others... They've done it.
29:
How EXCELLENT! Do you see that,
pipsqueak diviner? Stella and the
others are most incredible!
33:
Indeed... They're never content to
rest on their laurels...
38:
Look! Something's happening to the
dragon!
45:
Sure can. Now that's a sight for sore
sensors...
48: But... it's also kinda, like... sad. Y'know?
66:
Thank you... I'm guessing it was you
who brought Stella, Sho, and the
others?
71:
Well, actually, it was Sho who came
to MY rescue. Hehe.
75:
But that doesn't matter. We're all
safe! Leve, Nova, Stella—everyone!
86: That means this is all over...
95:
Does that make it an enemy? Do
we... have to fight it?
100:
It's not our enemy...
But we do need to fight it.
104: And for that... I'll need all of your help!
112:
I... always knew this wouldn't last
forever. I knew there would come a
time when we'd have to say
farewell...
115:
But until that very final moment... I
want you all to be by my side.
119: I want you to fight with me!
124:
Do you hear us, Dragon?
This is not the end!
